latestIgtvVideos.title: #ignorenomoreonline @maliniagarwal
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
“Do tag your favourite content creators who are facing so much online abuse”
They are an inspiration to so many they don’t deserve this!

Many a times I have been asked to avoid and ignore the abuse. But since the time I have started doing digital content I have started getting awful Comments and dms which were not only gross but dirty. 

So I decided that it is important to raise my voice so that this doesn't become a trend. 

Trolling is genderless, and it is important that we all should build together a safe place for each other

.
#ignorenomoreonline #trolling #missmalini #stalking #abuse #rapethreats #mentalhealth #accountability #womensafety #womenwhowrite #trollingcomments #nototrollaccounts #nomoretrolls #respecteachother #alwaysbekind❤️ #spreadpoaitivity #spreadawarness #bekindalways
